=Contact via Internet Relay Chat (IRC)=

Please note that IRC can be a low-traffic means of communication. There is active discussion periodically, but if asking for help, it could be a while before somebody answers, especially if most of the developers are on their sleepy time. Be patient and aware of [[IRC culture]].

==IRC network==

[[http://www.freenode.net|Freenode]] ([[irc://irc.freenode.net|irc.freenode.net]])

===Channels===

====Primary Channels====

* [[irc://irc.freenode.net/#sourcemage|#sourcemage]] - General IRC channel, all things Source Mage.
* [[irc://irc.freenode.net/#sourcemage-admin|#sourcemage-admin]] - Source Mage administrative channel. Meetings are held here.

====Project Components====

* [[irc://irc.freenode.net/#sourcemage-cauldron|#sourcemage-cauldron]] - Cauldron discussion (ISO Installer).
* [[irc://irc.freenode.net/#sourcemage-grimoire|#sourcemage-grimoire]] - A meeting place for the Grimoire Team members.
* [[irc://irc.freenode.net/#sourcemage-sorcery|#sourcemage-sorcery]] - All things sorcery related.
* [[irc://irc.freenode.net/#sourcemage-tome|#sourcemage-tome]] - A meeting place for the Tome Team members.

====On-Topic Spam/Dump====

* [[irc://irc.freenode.net/#sourcemage-commits|#sourcemage-commits]] - Source Code Management commit messages.
* [[irc://irc.freenode.net/#sourcemage-dump|#sourcemage-dump]] - Flood channel (for pasting code and output).

====Other On-Topic====

* [[irc://irc.freenode.net/#sourcemage-keysigning|#sourcemage-keysigning]] - Security Team PGP/GPG keysigning room.
* [[irc://irc.freenode.net/#sourcemage-quality|#sourcemage-quality]] - For the discussion of all things relating to Prometheus.
* [[irc://irc.freenode.net/#sourcemage-security|#sourcemage-security]] - A place to contact us and chat about security issues.
* [[irc://irc.freenode.net/#sourcemage-nosystemd|#sourcemage-nosystemd]] - Channel dedicated to systemd avoidance in Source Mage.

====Non-English====

* [[irc://irc.freenode.net/#sourcemagede|#sourcemagede]] - German users.
* [[irc://irc.freenode.net/#sourcemagefr|#sourcemagefr]] - French users.
* [[irc://irc.freenode.net/#sourcemageja|#sourcemageja]] - Japanese users.
* [[irc://irc.freenode.net/#sourcemagept|#sourcemagept]] - Portuguese users.
* [[irc://irc.freenode.net/#sourcemageru|#sourcemageru]] - Russian users.
* [[irc://irc.freenode.net/#sourcemagees|#sourcemagees]] - Spanish users.

====Off-Topic====

* [[irc://irc.freenode.net/#sourcemage-fun|#sourcemage-fun]] - Games and such.
* [[irc://irc.freenode.net/#sourcemage-politics|#sourcemage-politics]] - Where we send you when you start ranting about politics.